00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:17.525
Tea and shade, an introduction.

00:03:17.525 --> 00:03:18.900
And for me it's
a way of thinking

00:03:18.900 --> 00:03:24.060
about the embodiment of
the women in this era

00:03:24.060 --> 00:03:25.480
that they were living through--

00:03:25.480 --> 00:03:26.270
tea and shade.

00:03:26.270 --> 00:03:28.436
How many people are familiar
